WEBVTT

00:03.280 --> 00:04.080
Leave tonight

00:05.600 --> 00:06.240
First

00:06.760 --> 00:08.360
I am truly worried about Father's health

00:08.880 --> 00:09.360
Second

00:09.640 --> 00:10.520
Our dynasty values filial piety

00:10.720 --> 00:11.600
If I don't return

00:12.000 --> 00:13.760
I'm afraid it will give Prince Ning ammunition

00:14.200 --> 00:15.600
To criticize me in court

00:35.600 --> 00:36.200
Elder brother

00:37.200 --> 00:38.240
Father's health

00:38.760 --> 00:40.360
His Majesty is unwell

00:40.760 --> 00:41.760
Resting in a separate palace

00:42.840 --> 00:44.000
All palace affairs

00:44.480 --> 00:45.840
Are all handled by me

00:49.240 --> 00:49.760
Elder brother

00:51.360 --> 00:52.240
I want to see Father

00:59.760 --> 01:00.360
Second brother

01:01.760 --> 01:02.400
All these years

01:02.400 --> 01:03.760
You've been fighting with blades and swords

01:04.280 --> 01:05.480
You've been wild enough

01:07.000 --> 01:07.640
Today

01:07.760 --> 01:09.120
Let me welcome you back

01:11.880 --> 01:13.120
Elder brother, I want to see Father

01:15.000 --> 01:15.840
Elder brother, what are you doing?

01:18.520 --> 01:19.240
Sikong Zheng

01:32.880 --> 01:35.240
I really didn't want it to come to this

01:36.360 --> 01:37.120
But second brother

01:39.120 --> 01:41.080
You already have a foundation in the army

01:41.240 --> 01:42.520
How can I, the crown prince

01:43.240 --> 01:44.760
Sleep peacefully?
